Washington meetings on Israeli-Palestinian peace will be in favor
of the Palestinian side.
</P>
<P>
The sponsors of the meetings, namely U.S. and European leaders,
will "have a unified stand that they support the Palestinian
side," said Acting Information Minister Nasir Lawzi after a weekly
cabinet meeting Saturday.
</P>
<P>
