the paratroops of the IDF, where he had held a number of senior
command positions.
</P>
<P>
In 1993, he was appointed the IDF commander in the West
Bank. In 1994, he became the head of the southern command.
</P>
<P>
In 1996, he was named as the head of the planning branch of
the IDF. And last year, he was promoted to be the deputy chief of
general staff. 
