<HEADLINE> Pakistan PM Leaves for Almaty </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, May 10 (Xinhua) -- Pakistani Prime Minister Nawaz
Sharif left Lahore, provincial capital of Punjab, Sunday morning
for Almaty, Kazakhstan, to attend the sixth Economic Cooperation
Organization (ECO) Summit.
</P>
