the U.S. proposal on Israeli troop redeployment in the West Bank,
said a senior official.
</P>
<P>
The official, who spoke on condition of anonymity, made the
remarks to Xinhua here on Sunday to confirm the reports that the
Washington summit has been postponed.
</P>
<P>
