<DOCNO> XIE19980510.0139 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-05-10 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Hu Jintao Makes Important Speech on Criterion of Truth (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The reform and opening in the past two decades has been a process
of constantly pursuing emancipation of the mind and seeking truth from
facts.
</P>
<P>
In all the work of the reform and opening, and the
modernization drive, Deng Xiaoping always advocated emancipating
the mind and seeking truth from facts, and our Party also
consistently held up the principle. Therefore, the ideological
line of Marxism has struck deeper in the hearts of the people, the
basic theory of Marxism has been closely combined with the
specific situation of modern China, and the socialist reform and
opening, and modernization drive has been consistently forging
ahead.
</P>
<P>
In May 1980 Deng said that whether a socialist economic policy is
correct or not, in the final analysis, is decided by the
development of the productive forces and the increase of the
people's income, and this is the most fundamental criterion.
</P>
<P>
In the spring of 1992 Deng pointed out during his tour of south
China: The criterion of judging the work of each side must take
into account whether it is favorable for the development of
the productive forces of socialist society, favorable for the
increase of the comprehensive strength of the socialist state and
favorable for increasing the people's living standard.
</P>
<P>
Deng's speech during his tour of south China was a manifesto
that stuck to the theory and line since the Third Plenary Session
of the 11th CPC Central Committee and took the reform and opening,
and the modernization drive to a new stage in the significant
historical point at which China was experiencing the test of
political turmoil both worldwide and at home.
</P>
<P>
His speech gave a profound answer to many ideological questions
that had confined people's minds for a long time and offered new and
powerful ideological weapons with which we can grasp opportunities
and push ahead with the cause of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
