<HEADLINE> Hu Jintao Makes Important Speech on Criterion of Truth (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The process of emancipating the mind and socialist
modernization construction in the past two decades has enabled us
to accumulate rich experience and offered us much deep-rooted
enlightenment on how to adhere to the ideological line of Marxism.
</P>
<P>
First of all, adhering to the ideological line of emancipating
the mind and seeking truth from facts demands that we approach
Marxism with a scientific attitude.
</P>
<P>
Secondly, adhering to the ideological line of emancipating the
mind and seeking truth from facts demands that we respect the
practice of millions of people, and consistently verify theories,
lines and various principles and policies with practice.
</P>
<P>
Thirdly, adhering to the ideological line of emancipating the
mind and seeking truth from facts demands a deeper understanding
of China's national conditions, and unswerving procedure from the
actual conditions of the primary stage of socialism.
</P>
<P>
Fourthly, adhering to the ideological line of emancipating the
mind and seeking truth from facts needs a world-embracing vision,
attention to the study of the international economy, politics,
science and technology, and culture in contemporary times, the
ability to grasp the historical trends, and the ability to take
the lead as the times demand.
</P>
<P>
Finally, adhering to the ideological line of emancipating the
mind and seeking truth from facts demands that we vigorously build
up socialist democratic politics.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
