<HEADLINE> Hu Jintao Makes Important Speech on Criterion of Truth (5) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Now we are at an important historical period at the turn of the
century and a critical period to overcome the difficulties in
reform and achieve development. Today it is important for us to
commemorate the 20th anniversary of the debate on the criterion for
verifying truth.
</P>
<P>
On the basis of summing up past experiences, we should more
conscientiously and even more staunchly stick to the criterion of
practice, stick to the Party's ideological line of mind
emancipation and seeking truth from facts, so that our thinking
can be raised to the level of the requirements of the 15th
National Congress of the CPC and the requirements of the times.
</P>
<P>
First, we should be more conscientious and staunch in upholding
the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory and start a new tide of
studying the Theory.
</P>
<P>
Secondly, guided by this scientific theory, we should be bold
in practice and exploration to deal with the new issues and new
contradictions with the spirit of mind emancipation and seeking
truth from facts.
</P>
<P>
In our effort to promote sustained, rapid and sound growth of
the national economy, at present we face many new issues such as
the reforms concerning state-owned enterprises, financial system
and other sectors, economic restructuring, and better opening to
the outside world.
</P>
<P>
As regards these issues, the CPC Central Committee, with
Comrade Jiang Zemin at the core, put forward important ideas and
methods. We must keep pace with, have an in-depth understanding of
and get a correct grasp of them, both theoretically and in
practice. At the same time, we must continue to make explorations
in our practice and conscientiously resolve practical problems.
</P>
<P>
Thirdly, we should, according to the requirements of the 15th
CPC National Congress, unswervingly adhere to Deng Xiaoping Theory
and continue to enrich and creatively develop it in our practice.
</P>
<P>
The biggest theoretical role of the debate on the criterion of
verifying truth 20 years ago was that it restored the ideological
line of mind emancipation and seeking truth from facts. The
biggest theoretical achievement of our Party in the past 20 years
is the emergence of Deng Xiaoping Theory, which provides a
fundamental ideological and political guarantee for us to realize
the grand goal of building socialist modernization.
</P>
<P>
In the course of the debate 20 years ago and the following
reform and opening-up process over the past 20 years, ideological
theorists and journalists have made important contributions. In
the new situation, we should carry on the spirit of being bold in
exploration and make new contributions in theoretical study,
theoretical research and theoretical popularization.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
