<HEADLINE> Amphetamines Smuggled Into Thailand From Myanmar: Report </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, May 10 (Xinhua) -- As many as 12 million amphetamine
tablets are smuggled into Thailand from Myanmar each day,
according to a report Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The pills are being smuggled into Thailand through many border
points in northern Thailand's provinces of Chiang Mai, Mae Hong
Son and Chiang Rai, said Thongchai Chaiprom, a coordinator of the
Northern Bureau of the Office of Narcotics Control Board.
